column2: This spreadsheet is intended for token teams to disclose token distribution details. Instructions and an example on how distribution details can be shared is shown below.
1. Make a copy of this spreadsheet under File > Make a Copy
2. Replace sample data in Requirements (C) with applicable data
3. Share the completed spreadsheet (Google Sheets [preferred] or Excel file are accepted)
For top 20 wallets AND team/development/foundation wallets, airdrop/distribution holdings, marketing funds, vesting funds or any locked up supply.
